name: ROCK INVASION VR
summary: Play Rock Invasion VR, a guitar focused rock VR rhythm music game that mixes rock concert fantasy with alien-blasting arcade action against an extraterrestrial invasion, on Meta Quest 2 & 3. Hit colored notes, strum in time, fire laser beams from your guitar to destroy UFOs, protect the stage, master multiple difficulty levels, compete for high scores and enjoy an original indie rock soundtrack with no extra peripherals.
